# Swinging ship (swinging_ship flat ride): the boat + swing beams only.
# Authored hanging from the OBJ origin (the swing axis) so animation.frames
# can swing it about +Z and lift the pivot onto the base-game A-frame. The
# supports are base-game graphics, so the object provides only the ship;
# 2 camera planes x 19 swing poses (+8 blank rider slots each).
# OBJ space: +X forward, +Y up, +Z right; origin at footprint-base centre.
mtllib materials.mtl

